    "title": "Modules/Technology Used:",
    "content": ". | Peripheral Modules . | SYS Time | SYSTICK | Timer | SERCOM(I2C) | SERCOM(USART) | EIC | . | Driver Modules . | BM71 Driver | . | STDIO Library | . ",
