    "title": "Hardware Used:",
    "content": ". | PIC32CM MC00 Curiosity Nano Evaluation Kit | Curiosity Nano Base for click boards | BM71-XPRO | Fan Click | 5V DC Fan | Lipo Rechargeable Battery | . ",
