    "title": "Comments:",
    "content": ". | This application demo builds and works out of box by following the instructions above in “Running the Demo” section. If you need to enhance/customize this application demo, you need to use the MPLAB Harmony v3 Software framework. Refer links below to setup and build your applications using MPLAB Harmony. | How to Setup MPLAB Harmony v3 Software Development Framework | How to Build an Application by Adding a New PLIB, Driver, or Middleware to an Existing MPLAB Harmony v3 Project | . | . Revision: . | v1.3.0 released demo application | . ",
