    "title": "Hardware Used:",
    "content": ". | SAM E54 Curiosity Ultra Development Board | AC328904 - PIC32 Audio Codec Daughter Card | maXTouch® Curiosity Pro Board | Micro SD Card | USB Thumb Drive | . ",
